DELETE the server folder

Open terminal in vscode and run:
(ctrl + `) 


mkdir server

(Download the file and Add the server.js file in this folder.)

Open terminal in vscode and run the ff:
cd server
npm init -y
npm install express 

npm install cors body-parser mysql nodemon
npm install cookie-parser jsonwebtoken bcrypt



On the package.json file:

below main server.js add this:

"type": "module", 

sa scripts{} naman:
"start": "node server.js",
"devStart": "nodemon server.js"

OUTPUT OF PACKAGE.JSON SHOULD LOOK LIKE THE IMG ATTACHED.
